casebody.data:
Paris PALMER
v.
COMMISSIONER OF CORRECTION Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided February 7, 2017

Peter G. Billings, assigned counsel, in support of the petition.

Jennifer F. Miller, deputy assistant state's attorney, in opposition.

The petitioner Paris Palmer's petition for certification for appeal from the Appellate Court, 170 Conn. App. 903, 152 A.3d 580 (2017), is denied.
